# Images Directory

Place your documentation images here:

## App Screenshots
- `app-logo.png` - App logo
- `main-screen.png` - Main screen with Zmanim
- `settings.png` - Settings interface
- `classes.png` - Classes schedule
- `memorial.png` - Memorial/yahrzeit page
- `schedule.png` - Prayer schedule
- `backgrounds.png` - Background customization options
- `messages.png` - Messages/announcements
- `zmanim.png` - Zmanim display
- `hebrew-calendar.png` - Hebrew calendar features

## Setup Screenshots
- `create-gist.png` - Creating a GitHub Gist
- `token-scopes.png` - Token permission scopes
- `app-gist-settings.png` - App Gist configuration

## Recommended Sizes
- App logo: 512x512px
- Screenshots: 1080x1920px (portrait) or 1920x1080px (landscape)
- Keep file sizes under 1MB each

## Format
- Use PNG for screenshots (better quality)
- Use WebP for smaller file sizes
- Optimize images before committing

